org.net4care.skype.util

Class ParseSkypeKitVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.net4care.skype.util.ParseSkypeKitVersion

  • public class ParseSkypeKitVersion
extends Object
    Tutorial SkypeKit Version Parse Object. Encapsulates obtaining and parsing of the SkypeKit version string returned by com.skype.api.Skype.GetVersionString.

    Static methods enable you to obtain the:
    • major version number
    • minor version number
    • patch version number
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Andrea Drane

    • Constructor Detail

      • ParseSkypeKitVersion

        public ParseSkypeKitVersion(com.skype.api.Skype mySkype)
        Tutorial constructor.

        Obtain the skypeKit version string, for example: 
         
 2.0/windows-x86-skypekit-novideo_3.1.0.2689_125068
        and:
        • store it in versionStr
        • split it at the underscores, yielding "2.0/windows-x86-skypekit-novideo", "3.1.0.2689", and "125068"
        • split the version number segment at the periods, yielding "3", "1", "0", and "2689"
        • store the number of version number components in versionNumCnt
        • store the actual version number components in versionNums
        Since:
        1.0
